## Before deploying any container, verify your host environment permissions.

Check Docker Service
Bash

sudo systemctl status docker

Phase 1: Persistent Storage
Bash
docker pull lscr.io/linuxserver/brave:latest
mkdir -p ~/brave-config

Phase 2: Deployment

Bash
docker run -d \
  --name=brave-browser \
  --security-opt seccomp=unconfined \
  -e PUID=1000 \
  -e PGID=1000 \
  -e TZ=Etc/UTC \
  -p 3002:3000 \
  -p 3003:3001 \
  -v ~/brave-config:/config \
  --shm-size="1gb" \
  --restart unless-stopped \
  lscr.io/linuxserver/brave:latest
